🔴 KRITIK: 4-LAYER API ARXITEKTURASI (HEECH QACHON BUZILMASLIGI KERAK)
   Infrastructure (httpClient.ts) → Service (*.service.ts) → Hook (*.hooks.ts) → UI Component
   
   🚫 TA'QIQLANADI:
      - Component ichida httpClient/axios chaqirish
      - Service ichida React hook (useAuthStore) import qilish
      - Server ma'lumotlarini Zustand persist da saqlash
      - Raw hex ranglar ishlatish (CSS variable ishlat)
   
   ✅ TO'G'RI:
      - Component → Hook → Service → httpClient
      - Ma'lumot transformatsiyasi Service layerda
      - TS interface hamma API request/response uchun

📋 MAJBURIY TEXNOLOGIYALAR:
   - Server State: @tanstack/react-query (useQuery/useMutation)
   - Client State: Zustand + persist middleware (src/store/)
   - Forms: react-hook-form + zod validation
   - Icons: lucide-react
   - Styling: Tailwind CSS (faqat CSS variables bg-background, text-foreground va h.k.)
   - UI: shadcn/ui (@/components/ui/*)
   - HTTP: axios (faqat src/services/httpClient.ts orqali)
   - Routing: react-router-dom

📁 FILE NAMING:
   - kebab-case: employee.service.ts, auth.hooks.ts, new-order-dialog.tsx
   - Domain guruhlash: src/pages/<Domain>/{index.tsx, types.ts, components/}

📚 SESSIYA BOSHLANGANDA:
   1. AVVAL AI_GUIDELINES.md ni o'qi (to'liq qoidalar uchun)
   2. Keyin vazifani bajarishga kirish
   3. Har bir kod yozishdan oldin 5.1 Pre-Task Verification checklist ni bajar

